Tarah Lynne Schaeffer https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tarah_Lynne_Schaeffer 0 Tarah Lynne Schaeffer (born July 4, 1984) is an American actress. She is known for her role on Sesame Street.She was cast in 1993 as the first Sesame Street cast member with disabilities – she was born with a disorder called osteogenesis imperfecta. She remained on the show for eight seasons. Tarah_Lynne_Schaeffer ( born July_4_,_1984 ) is an_American_actress .
